Xu Beihong Painting Sells for Record $42 Million, Xinhua Reports

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-12-06T14:46:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-06/xu-beihong-painting-sells-for-record-42-million-xinhua-reports.html
A painting by Chinese artist Xu
Beihong sold for 266.8 million yuan ($42 million) at an auction
in Beijing, setting a record for the modern Chinese painter,
Xinhua News Agency said, citing the sale results.  The previous top price for a work by Xu, who died in 1953,
was 171 million yuan, the official news agency reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  